  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Horde Survival is an arena bullet hell game where survival is the main goal. Play alone or online with up to 4 players to fight off waves of monsters as you try to survive the current wave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/ba80d1a3ffc1ae08f58b3e0ef903f802.avif?t=1736589114\" width=500 height=135 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from several playable characters (Wizard, Warrior, Warlock, Ranger, Paladin, and Dark Knight, Fatty, Princess). Each character has its own unique spells to learn as well as other common spells that are available to them also. Each character benefits from stats differently, creating unique runs between characters. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/222edd37b83fb6bd6d1aea5b62a43a40.poster.avif?t=1736589114\" width=600 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/222edd37b83fb6bd6d1aea5b62a43a40.webm?t=1736589114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/222edd37b83fb6bd6d1aea5b62a43a40.mp4?t=1736589114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/6bdd2ec6176e120787bf9e7282a20434.avif?t=1736589114\" width=625 height=169 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless amount of waves that become progressively harder, challenging the player to be quick on their feet and think strategically when picking new spells or stats. The hordes of monsters don't stop coming until the player dies or decides to call it quits. Try running different builds, the only limitation is your imagination and see how far you can survive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/ccf284d7e5c2ac6b0d16409d25337fc9.avif?t=1736589114\" width=625 height=169 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 4 players in online co-op. Work together and see how long your team can survive the hordes of monsters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/d3852ab13d36c5f3b60ed032fca6a2ec.avif?t=1736589114\" width=625 height=169 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight unique boss battles that occur during certain waves. Each boss battle comes with unique mechanics that keep you on your toes. Defeating a boss(Stone Golem, Witch, etc.) will grant the player guaranteed loot. But get defeated by them and your run comes to an end. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/21b68ad18045c396b1884c3669c3c0ac.poster.avif?t=1736589114\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/21b68ad18045c396b1884c3669c3c0ac.webm?t=1736589114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/21b68ad18045c396b1884c3669c3c0ac.mp4?t=1736589114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/ebd1c50a1acf70b60955219811c3c159.avif?t=1736589114\" width=625 height=169 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armor galore! More than one hundred pieces of armor that you can choose from (Common, Rare, Epic, and Legendary). Each armor piece has its own unique set of stats that the player can benefit from.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/b39b37ddcea2a7a05411754acf80ec11.avif?t=1736589114\" width=625 height=169 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clearing a wave gives the player the opportunity of buying stats or spells. There are hundreds of buffs and several spells that each character can choose from(Thunder, Beams, Shockwaves, Blackhole, etc.). But beware there is a limit in the amount of spells that can be learnt, so pick wisely what spells you want to have in your arsenal.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/28ee40580410a036816c6c96820cfe78.poster.avif?t=1736589114\" width=600 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/28ee40580410a036816c6c96820cfe78.webm?t=1736589114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738910/extras/28ee40580410a036816c6c96820cfe78.mp4?t=1736589114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
